    <h2>2. Content and Data Sources</h2>
    <p>All questions, answers, and image assets used in this app are based on <strong>publicly available and government-provided materials</strong> for driving theory tests.</p>

    <ul>
        <li>The content is intended for educational and practice purposes only</li>
        <li>We do not claim ownership of official government materials</li>
        <li>All materials are used to help users prepare for driving exams</li>
    </ul>

