    <p>These services may collect limited, non-personal technical data according to their own privacy policies.</p>

    <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
    <p>Since the app does not collect personal data, no personal information is stored or processed by the app.</p>

    <h2>5. Children’s Privacy</h2>
    <p>This app is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect any data from children.</p>

    <h2>6. Disclaimer</h2>
